column5: Is there still a ramp at Port Maitland.  Going to go down tonight and give it a try around 5 ish.  Also does anyone know if the walleye are co operating? Thanks Jeff
Yes I believe there is still a free ramp there, and from what I hear the smaller walleye are still hitting in the river and bigger ones out in the lake.
Lots of Mud cats hitting everything in the river right now,  and yes the ramp is still free in Port Maitland.
